c: 46
v: 17
t: "Kala non wi'an…óo jibim…ìe mo …ìen: \"Uf mo'on ! Kere on foday lam immintineede hara le gom…óii mofte yawtiino ado lam?\" Hara …ìen …ói…óo no faabtinora Allah [wiide mo]: \"Ee bone maa, Gom…óin ! Pellet, fodooree Allah nde ko goonga\". O wi'a: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa tinndi adinoo…ìe …ìen"